mmary%22%3A%22There%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bno%20requirement%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20withhold%20the%20Reuters'%20X%20handle%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20said%2C%20denying%20any%20role%20in%20the%20international%20news%20agency's%20social%20media%20account%20being%20withheld%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-responds-after-news-agency-reuters-x-account-withheld-in-india-8832207%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Welcome%20to%20Silicon%20Valley's%20winner-take-all%20era%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Person%20carrying%20golden%20Meta%20check%20under%20their%20arm%20with%20a%20person%20holding%20their%20hand%20out%20with%20the%20corner%20of%20the%20check%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6866d7d585e81483682d6154%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C2%A0%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Ava%20Horton%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E100%20million-dollar%20pay%20packages%20aren't%20just%20for%20the%20Shohei%20Ohtanis%20and%20Cristiano%20Ronaldos%20of%20the%20world%20anymore.%20In%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fin-silicon-valley-it-is-the-summer-of-fomo-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enine-figure%20pay%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20reportedly%20now%20being%20floated%20to%20the%20world's%20top%20talent%20as%20the%20race%20to%20own%20AI%20enters%20a%20new%20frenzied%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20has%20made%20at%20least%2010%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-meta-tried-poaching-openai-staff-ai-talent-war-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-pay%20offers%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20up%20to%20%24300%20million%20over%20four%20years%20to%20top%20OpenAI%20researchers%20for%20what%20it's%20calling%20its%20Superintelligence%20Lab%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-offer-top-ai-talent-300-million%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWired%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20this%20week.%20Sam%20Altman%20claimed%20in%20June%20that%20OpenAI%20workers%20had%20been%20offered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-meta-tried-poaching-openai-staff-ai-talent-war-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24100%20million%20signing%20bonuses%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20jump%20ship.%20Meta%20spokesman%20Andy%20Stone%20called%20news%20of%20the%20reported%20pay%20%26quot%3Buntrue%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20%26quot%3Bthe%20size%20and%20structure%20of%20these%20compensation%20packages%20have%20been%20misrepresented%20all%20over%20the%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20actual%20figures%20are%2C%20it%20seems%20a%20select%20few%20researchers%20could%20see%20bank%20account%20balances%20that%20rival%20or%20surpass%20CEOs%20at%20other%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20would%20out-earn%20other%20tech%20workers%20by%20numbers%20that%20are%20hard%20to%20envision.%20(A%20BI%20analysis%20of%20Meta's%20federal%20filings%20last%20week%20found%20that%20software%20engineers%20at%20the%20company%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-salaries-what-it-pays-ai-engineers-researchers-compensation-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20up%20to%20%24480%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20base%20salary.)%20A%20former%20Meta%20engineer%20who%20still%20works%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20told%20us%20that%20as%20%26quot%3Btop%20tech%20talent%20is%20finally%20being%20treated%20like%20top%20sports%26quot%3B%20many%20of%20tech's%20rank%20and%20file%20workers%20are%20filled%20with%20resentment%20and%20jealousy%2C%20%26quot%3Bespecially%20amongst%20folks%20that%20have%20been%20in%20the%20industry%20a%20while.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemand%20for%20AI%20experts%20far%20outpaces%20the%20supply.%20Whatever%20enticing%20salaries%20Meta%20is%20actually%20offering%20must%20be%20outsized%20enough%20that%20they%20tempt%20people%20to%20abandon%20the%20sleek%2C%20hotbed%20of%20AI%20innovation%20to%20take%20on%20the%20task%20of%20bringing%20Meta%2C%20a%20company%20that%20bet%20everything%20on%20the%20metaverse%2C%20through%20yet%20another%20rebrand.%20To%20achieve%20Mark%20Zuckerberg's%20dream%20of%20building%20a%20personalized%20AI%20for%20everyone%2C%20Meta%20no%20doubt%20needs%20to%20open%20its%20wallet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20seems%20to%20be%20testing%20now%20how%20many%20zeros%20he%20needs%20to%20put%20on%20a%20check%20to%20get%20people%20to%20come%20play%20for%20his%20team.%20But%20perhaps%20more%20than%20anything%2C%20the%20eye-popping%20salaries%20underscore%20how%20the%20divide%20between%20top%20AI%20talent%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20is%20becoming%20not%20just%20a%20gap%2C%20but%20a%20chasm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20make%20sense%20for%20engineers%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20experienced%20and%20with%20great%20credentials%2C%20to%20make%20NBA%20players'%20salaries%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Natalia%20Luka%2C%20who%20studies%20economic%20sociology%2C%20organizations%2C%20and%20science%20and%20technology%20at%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley.%20The%20%26quot%3Bexorbitant%20sums%26quot%3B%20that%20tech%20companies%20are%20paying%2C%20%26quot%3Bnot%20just%20for%20AI%20engineers%2C%20but%20also%20the%20computing%20power%2C%20the%20data%20centers%2C%20all%20of%20those%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20is%20putting%20enormous%20%26quot%3Bpressure%20on%20them%20to%20cut%20costs%20elsewhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20top%20AI%20employees%20have%20humungous%20offer%20letters%20sent%20their%20way%2C%20thousands%20of%20tech%20employees%20are%20watching%20their%20job%20security%20crumble.%20Microsoft%20announced%20last%20week%20that%20it%20will%20lay%20off%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-layoffs-major-round-managers-workers-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E9%2C000%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20(with%20the%20sales%20and%20Xbox%20divisions%20among%20those%20affected)%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20number%20of%20cuts%20at%20the%20company%20so%20far%20this%20year%20to%20about%2015%2C000.%20These%20come%20as%20tech%20companies%20have%20spent%20nearly%20three%20years%20culling%20their%20ranks%20after%20overhiring%20and%20hoarding%20talent%20during%20the%20height%20of%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%20More%20than%20600%2C000%20tech%20workers%20have%20lost%20their%20jobs%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FLayoffs.fyi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELayoffs.fyi%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20tracking%20cuts%20in%20the%20industry%20in%202022.%20Tech%20jobs%20overall%2C%20however%2C%20have%20continued%20to%20grow%2C%20and%20are%20expected%20to%20do%20so%20twice%20as%20fast%20as%20other%20sectors%20over%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report%20from%20CompTIA%2C%20a%20trade%20association%20for%20the%20IT%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20disparity%20has%20alarmed%20many.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20this%20existential%20dread%20going%20around%20that%20the%20field%20is%20fundamentally%20changing%2C%20and%20the%20new%20entrants%20have%20had%20the%20rug%20pulled%20from%20under%20them%20as%20most%20companies%20are%20only%20hiring%20senior%20folks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Meta%20engineer%20told%20us.%20While%20that%20%26quot%3Bmakes%20sense%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20person%20added%2C%20they%20fear%20it%20%26quot%3Bis%20only%20going%20to%20make%20it%20impossible%20for%20them%20to%20grow%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20senior%20engineers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Meta%20insiders%20are%20deeply%20cynical%20about%20the%20new%20%26quot%3BSuperintelligence%26quot%3B%20organization%20led%20by%2028-year-old%20Alexandr%20Wang%20and%20recent%20hires%20from%20OpenAI%20and%20DeepMind.%20Screenshots%20from%20a%20group%20of%20Meta%20employees%20on%20Blind%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider%20show%20one%20employee%20calling%20the%20new%20group%20%26quot%3Bmarketing%20BS%20to%20feed%20the%20media.%26quot%3B%20Some%20are%20concerned%20that%20Meta's%20current%20GenAI%20org%20will%20be%20sidelined%20or%20laid%20off%2C%20with%20one%20post%20asking%2C%20%26quot%3BShould%20I%20switch%20away%20from%20GenAI%3F%20I%20feel%20like%20we're%20all%20going%20to%20get%20fired.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20everywhere%20have%20increasingly%20made%20investments%20and%20pivots%20to%20AI%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20and%20other%20workers%20have%20been%20cut%20to%20foot%20the%20bills.%20Meta%20bought%20nearly%20half%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-scale-ai-15-billion-alexandr-wang-acquihire-ai-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScale%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%20for%20%2414%20billion.%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20from%20Google%20to%20Meta%20have%20boasted%20about%20the%20ways%20they're%20using%20AI%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-anthropic-ai-llama-coding-efficiency-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrite%20code%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20become%20more%20efficient%2C%20all%20while%20the%20career%20ladder%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-ladder-software-engineers-collapsing-ai-google-meta-coding-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentry-level%20software%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%20topples.%20%26quot%3BYou%20probably%20have%20to%20assume%20that%20just%20given%20the%20intense%20focus%20on%20all%20things%20AI%20right%20now%2C%20that%20it%20does%20diminish%20other%20potential%20areas%20of%20innovation%2C%20other%20potential%20investments%2C%20and%20by%20extension%2C%20it%20probably%20is%20going%20to%20diminish%20other%20workers%20in%20some%20capacity%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Tim%20Herbert%2C%20chief%20research%20officer%20at%20CompTIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concurrent%20battle%20between%20Meta%20and%20OpenAI%20over%20the%20industry's%20most%20elite%20talent%20is%20far%20from%20the%20only%20one%20%E2%80%94%20companies%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20more%20for%20AI%20talent%20at%20much%20lower%20levels%2C%20too.%20As%20of%20April%202024%2C%20entry%20level%20AI%20engineers%20made%20about%208.5%25%20more%20than%20other%20engineers%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FLevels.fyi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELevels.fyi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Mid-%20and%20senior-level%20engineers%20earn%20about%2011%25%20more%20than%20similarly%20experienced%20engineers%20not%20working%20directly%20on%20AI.%20Demand%20for%20AI%20skills%20has%20grown%20by%2021%25%20annually%20since%202019%2C%20according%20to%20management%20consulting%20firm%20Bain%20%26amp%3B%20Company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everyone%20is%20mad%20about%20the%20pay%20gap.%20A%20current%20engineer%20in%20Meta's%20GenAI%20org%20told%20us%20they%20believe%20most%20people%20at%20the%20company%20understand%20the%20rationale%2C%20and%20even%20support%20it.%20%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20produce%20that%20kind%20of%20impact%20and%20hence%20do%20not%20deserve%20that%20kind%20of%20compensation%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20most%20Meta%20employees%20are%20pretty%20much%20on%20board%20with%20this.%20If%20this%20team%20delivers%20disproportionately%2C%20we%20all%20benefit%20via%20stocks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rush%20for%20AI%20talent%20isn't%20so%20different%20from%20other%20eras%20of%20rapid%20tech%20innovation%2C%20where%20few%20have%20the%20skills%20to%20perform%20highly%20sought%20after%20work%2C%20says%20Sonny%20Tambe%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20Wharton%20School%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania.%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20different%20now%20is%20that%20the%20pace%20is%20much%20faster%20and%20there%20could%20be%20outsized%20rewards%20for%20companies%20who%20win%20this%20market%2C%20so%20the%20stakes%20are%20unusually%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20Tambe%20says.%20%26quot%3BAI%20companies%20don't%20have%20time%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20talent%20pool%20to%20expand%2C%20and%20so%20the%20effect%20is%20more%20pronounced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20are%20skeptical%20that%20superstar%20athlete%20salaries%20will%20become%20the%20new%20norm%20for%20top%20AI%20talent%3B%20as%20more%20people%20are%20trained%20to%20lead%20generative%20AI%20teams%2C%20this%20may%20even%20become%20a%20passing%20fad.%20%26quot%3BThe%20market%20is%20going%20to%20adjust%20in%20terms%20of%20having%20credentialed%20people%20who%20can%20do%20this%20kind%20of%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Luka%20says.%20%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20it%20really%20is%20a%20fairly%20select%20group%20that%20knows%20how%20to%20run%20these%20giant%20AI%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20wait%20for%20more%20AI%20experts%20to%20emerge%2C%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20two-tier%20system%20splitting%20inside%20Meta.%20Workers%20on%20Blind%20are%20describing%20Superintelligence%20recruits%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20chosen%20few.%26quot%3B%20One%20employee%20sarcastically%20noted%20that%20those%20working%20in%20the%20GenAI%20org%20will%20%26quot%3Bget%20to%20label%20data%20for%20minimum%20wage.%26quot%3B%20Another%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BOnly%20a%20select%20few%20will%20get%20promoted%E2%80%A6%20this%20is%20the%20era%20of%20elite%20internal%20poaching.%26quot%3B%20Tech%20companies%20will%20still%20need%20to%20invest%20in%20other%20areas%20to%20move%20their%20goals%20forward.%20For%20now%2C%20it's%20a%20great%20time%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20few%20brightest%20brains%20on%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Famanda-hoover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAmanda%20Hoover%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20