0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20sent%20that%20to%20my%20agent%2C%20and%20I%20just%20typed%20in%20the%20text%20with%20the%20link%20to%20the%20story%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20stupid%3F%26quot%3B%20hoping%20he'd%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20stay%20away.%26quot%3B%20And%20hours%20later%2C%20my%20agent%20got%20back%20to%20me%2C%20and%20the%20ball%20started%20rolling.%20Be%20careful%20what%20you%20wish%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20I%20really%20enjoyed%20about%20%26quot%3BRebirth%26quot%3B%20is%20its%20stand-alone%20feel.%20Was%20that%20intentional%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20David%20Koepp's%20script.%20That's%20why%20I%20really%20liked%20it.%20What%20the%20best%20sequels%20have%20in%20common%20is%20that%20the%20first%20one%20didn't%20know%20it%20was%20part%20of%20a%20trilogy%20or%20the%20start%20of%20sequels.%20It%20was%20just%20this%20self-contained%20story.%20So%20that's%20the%20way%20to%20go%2C%20to%20try%20to%20tell%20the%20best%20film%20you%20can.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20then%20a%20high-class%20problem%20after%20that.%20And%20I'm%20not%20joking%2C%20but%20I%20haven't%20had%20a%20single%20conversation%20about%20a%20sequel%20with%20anyone%20from%20Universal%20or%20the%20producers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat%20was%20my%20follow-up.%20Nobody%20tapped%20you%20on%20the%20shoulder%20and%20suggested%20a%20more%20heavy-handed%20way%20to%20tease%20another%20movie%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo.%20It%20was%20even%20a%20joke%20with%20the%20actors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jurassic%20park%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f104bcd4dca68396f2342a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221296%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BJurassic%20Park.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EUniversal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20the%20movie%20also%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20nostalgia%2C%20with%20hat%20tips%20ranging%20from%20%26quot%3BJurassic%20Park%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3BJaws.%20%26quot%3B%20Did%20that%20come%20organically%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20got%20the%20script%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20magical%20ticket%20back%20to%20being%20a%20kid%20again.%20So%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20was%20already%20in%20there%2C%20and%20half%20of%20it%20I%20probably%20brought%20with%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20mean%2C%20you're%20making%20a%20movie%20for%20Amblin%20that%20features%20a%20giant%20creature%20in%20the%20water.%20Of%20course%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20lean%20into%20%26quot%3BJaws.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeah.%20The%20script%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey're%20chasing%20a%20giant%20dinosaur%20in%20the%20water%2C%20on%20a%20boat%2C%20with%20a%20rifle%20leading%20out%20the%20front%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20you're%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BGuys%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20you've%20ever%20seen%20this%20movie%20called%20'Jaws%2C'%20but%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20we%20escape%20those%20visuals.%26quot%3B%20So%20it%20was%20a%20difficult%20situation%2C%20and%20the%20only%20way%20I%20got%20through%20it%20was%20this%20being%20a%20giant%20love%20letter%20to%20Steven%20Spielberg.%20Whenever%20there's%20a%20gap%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20put%20something%20in%20that%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20something%20from%20his%20movies%20that%20we%20love.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20have%20now%20worked%20with%20two%20faces%20on%20the%20Mt.%20Rushmore%20of%20American%20cinema%2C%20George%20Lucas%20and%20Steven%20Spielberg.%20Compare%20and%20contrast%20working%20for%20them.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20George%20had%20retired%20when%20we%20started%20%26quot%3BRogue%20One%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20he%20was%20totally%20happy%20for%20us%20to%20go%20do%20our%20thing.%20But%20I%20did%20have%20the%20more%20surreal%20moment%20of%20showing%20him%20around%20the%20set%20of%20%26quot%3BRogue%20One.%26quot%3B%20But%20what%20I%20did%20to%20take%20the%20pressure%20off%20myself%2C%20seeing%20I%20was%20doing%20a%20%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%26quot%3B%20spin-off%2C%20I%20was%20competing%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20the%20holiday%20special%20and%20Caravan%20of%20Courage%2C%20the%20Ewok%20adventure.%20So%20I%20jokingly%20framed%20those%20movie%20posters%20in%20my%20office%20as%20a%20reminder%20to%20me%20that%20I%20just%20have%20to%20do%20better%20than%20those.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20one%20day%20I%20was%20told%20George%20is%20here%2C%20and%20he%20just%20walked%20into%20the%20office%2C%20and%20I%20was%20blown%20away.%20And%20as%20I%20was%20talking%20to%20him%2C%20I%20realized%20the%20posters%20on%20the%20wall.%20So%20I'm%20trying%20to%20be%20as%20animated%20as%20possible%20so%20he%20wouldn't%20look%20at%20the%20wall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteven%20developed%20the%20story%20with%20David%2C%20so%20he%20was%20fully%20engaged%20from%20the%20start.%20He%20was%20in%20the%20meetings%20during%20preproduction.%20He%20would%20call%20me%20when%20I%20started%20shooting.%20He%20watched%20the%20dallies%20every%20day.%20We%20even%20sent%20him%20the%20first%20cut%20of%20the%20movie.%20I%20would%20have%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20phone%20calls%20with%20him%20giving%20me%20feedback.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWere%20you%20prepared%20he'd%20be%20so%20hands-on%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20definitely%20the%20right%20amount%2C%20but%20going%20in%20I%20didn't%20know%20if%20I'd%20see%20him%20once%20or%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20it%20was%20going%20to%20play%20out.%20And%20I%20remember%20on%20day%20one%2C%20the%20first%20meeting%20at%20Universal%2C%20I%20get%20there%20early%2C%20and%20the%20next%20person%20who%20walked%20in%20was%20Steven%20Spielberg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20never%20forget%20the%20first%20interaction%20I%20ever%20had%20with%20him.%20It%20was%20right%20after%20%26quot%3BGodzilla.%26quot%3B%20I%20got%20an%20email%20from%20%5B%26quot%3BThe%20Lord%20of%20the%20Rings%26quot%3B%20creator%5D%20Peter%20Jackson%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20video%20attached.%20I%20hit%20play%20and%20it's%20Steven%20Spielberg.%20Peter%20Jackson%20was%20filming%20Steven%20Spielberg%20at%20George%20Lucas'%20birthday%20party.%20Steven%20had%20just%20seen%20%26quot%3BGodzilla%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20saying%20really%20nice%20things%20about%20it%2C%20so%20Peter%20sent%20it%20to%20me.%20I%20watched%20it%20and%20collapsed%20and%20burst%20into%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20moments%20as%20a%20filmmaker%20where%20everything%20you're%20doing%20in%20your%20life%2C%20you%20ask%2C%20Why%20am%20I%20doing%20this%3F%20What%20is%20the%20goal%3F%20You%20don't%20know.%20That%20is%20the%20answer%20to%20why%20I'm%20doing%20this%3B%20for%20that%20moment%2C%20for%20that%20little%20video.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rogue%20One%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5eaae72c144192640b435c24%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BRogue%20One%3A%20A%20Star%20Wars%20Story.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EWalt%20Disney%20Studios%20Motion%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe're%20coming%20close%20to%2010%20years%20of%20%26quot%3BRogue%20One%26quot%3B%20coming%20out%20in%20theaters.%20Do%20you%20appreciate%20your%20contribution%20to%20%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%26quot%3B%3F%20It's%20arguably%20the%20best%20%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%26quot%3B%20movie%20since%20Disney%20bought%20Lucasfilm%2C%20and%20it's%20up%20there%20as%20one%20of%20the%20best%20out%20of%20all%20the%20movies.%20Can%20you%20appreciate%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20agree%20with%20it%2C%20but%20I%20appreciate%20it.%20I'm%20very%20grateful%20that%20people%20say%20nice%20things.%20But%20what's%20super%20interesting%20about%20it%2C%20which%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20in%20your%20pocket%20as%20you%20go%20through%20making%20other%20films%2C%20is%20that%20it's%20not%20about%20how%20people%20feel%20the%20day%20it%20gets%20released%2C%20it's%20how%20people%20feel%20about%20it%2010%2C%2020%20years%20from%20now.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20make%20a%20movie%2C%20you're%20living%20at%20least%20a%20year%20from%20now.%20You're%20trying%20to%20imagine%20what%20it's%20like%2C%20all%20these%20decisions%20you're%20making%2C%20what%20they%20are%20going%20to%20be%20like%20a%20year%20from%20now%20when%20this%20movie%20is%20released.%20What's%20the%20audience%20going%20to%20think%3F%20And%20as%20the%20movie%20comes%20out%2C%20you%20go%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20pretend%20I'm%20living%2010%20years%20from%20now%20and%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20people%20say%20in%20the%20moment.%26quot%3B%20It's%20the%20kid%20who%20comes%20up%20to%20you%2020%20years%20from%20now%20and%20goes%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20god%2C%20I%20loved%20that%20movie!%26quot%3B%20I%20think%20that's%20the%20reward.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWould%20you%20ever%20go%20down%20that%20road%20of%20doing%20%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%26quot%3B%20again%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20thing%20that%20was%20in%20my%20life%20before%20I%20knew%20what%20a%20film%20was.%20And%20so%20it's%20like%20your%20mom%3B%20it's%20like%20something%20so%20a%20part%20of%20you.%20I'm%20always%20fascinated%20by%20what%20they're%20doing.%20I%20never%20stop%20loving%20that%20trilogy%2C%20but%20I'm%20very%20happy%20to%20move%20on%20and%20do%20my%20thing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20interview%20has%20been%20condensed%20and%20edited%20for%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjurassic-world-rebirth-director-gareth-edwards-rogue-one-steven-spielberg-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751727003000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6865383af748d8c055f4cd4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjurassic-world-rebirth-director-gareth-edwards-ro