reat%20to%20both%20snow%20leopards%20and%20wolves%2C%20and%20the%20situation%20will%20only%20worsen%20if%20left%20unchecked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfrastructure%20development%20also%20risks%20fragmenting%20important%20corridors%20that%20connect%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20snow%20leopards%20to%20populations%20across%20Tibet%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20the%20Karakoram.%20Its%20distinct%20ecological%20and%20cultural%20identity%20calls%20for%20context-specific%20development.%20One-size-fits-all%20models%20from%20elsewhere%20are%20unlikely%20to%20work%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20model%20for%20the%20Himalayas%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEncouragingly%2C%20the%20survey%20aligns%20with%20international%20frameworks%20like%20PAWS%20(Population%20Assessment%20of%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Snow%20Leopards)%2C%20offering%20a%20model%20that%20can%20be%20replicated%20across%20the%20Himalayas.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20about%20tracking%20snow%20leopards%2C%20the%20same%20data%20and%20methods%20can%20be%20used%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F159407%2Fmaharashtra-hc-tiger-activists%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonitor%20other%20rare%20carnivores%3C%2Fa%3E%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-04T160257.690_11zon-1751625192.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Namgail%20says%20the%20felines%20are%20fondly%20called%20'Ri%20Gyancha'%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98ornaments%20of%20the%20mountains%E2%80%99%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20SetMyTrip%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025