20this%20law%2C%20once%20a%20woman%20got%20married%2C%20anything%20she%20owned%20%E2%80%94%20money%2C%20land%2C%20jewellery%2C%20automatically%20belonged%20to%20her%20husband.%20She%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20sell%20it%2C%20invest%20it%2C%20or%20use%20it%20independently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Act%20changed%20that.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F185674%2Findia-women-rights-property-inheritance-law-buying%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIt%20legally%20recognised%20a%20married%20woman%E2%80%99s%20right%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20hold%20property%20in%20her%20own%20name.%20She%20could%20now%20have%20legal%20ownership%20over%20her%20earnings%20and%20belongings%2C%20even%20while%20being%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20early%20attempt%20to%20say%3A%20a%20woman%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20extension%20of%20her%20husband.%20She%20has%20a%20legal%20identity.%20She%20can%20earn%2C%20own%2C%20and%20control.%20A%20quietly%20radical%20move%20for%20a%20society%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20think%20women%20needed%20bank%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20The%20Child%20Marriage%20Restraint%20Act%20(Sarda%20Act)%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%3A%201929%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%3A%20All%20of%20British%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChild%20marriage%20was%20not%20just%20common%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20the%20norm.%20Girls%20were%20married%20off%20before%20they%20even%20hit%20puberty.%20The%20Sarda%20Act%2C%20named%20after%20judge%20and%20reformer%20Harbilas%20Sarda%2C%20was%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20real%20attempt%20to%20put%20an%20age%20limit%20on%20this%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184503.761-1751548608.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Child%20marriage%20was%20abolished%20by%20a%20law%20that%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184503.761-1751548608.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184503.761-1751548608-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184503.761-1751548608-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184503.761-1751548608-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-03T184503.761-1751548608-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-461638%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChild%20marriage%20was%20abolished%20by%20a%20law%20that%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism.%20Picture%20source%3A%20garystockbridge%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20made%20it%20illegal%20for%20girls%20under%2014%20and%20boys%20under%2018%20to%20marry%20(later%20raised%20to%2018%20and%2021).%20Of%20course%2C%20implementation%20was%20patchy.%20But%20the%20message%20was%20clear%3A%20girls%20were%20not%20commodities%20to%20be%20handed%20over%20like%20dowry%20items.%20They%20deserved%20a%20childhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20law%20planted%20the%20seed%20for%20future%20reforms%20and%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20government%20stepping%20into%20personal%2C%20cultural%20territory%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy%20then%2C%20and%20still%20isn%E2%80%99t%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20The%20Hindu%20Succession%20Act%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%3A%201956%2C%20Amended