ink%20so%20too.%20His%20slice-of-life%20film%20%3Cem%3EI%20Want%20to%20Talk%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20an%20emotionally%20beguiling%20story%20of%20the%20complexities%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F450225%2Fterror-attacks-in-mumbai-26-11-hemant-karkare-anti-terrorism-squad-jui-karkare-navare-memoir%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efather-daughter%20dynamic%20%3C%2Fa%3Ejuxtaposed%20against%20the%20father%E2%80%99s%20medical%20diagnosis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Farjun-sen-and-battling-cancer-3-1751550919.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Arjun%20with%20Abhishek%20Bachchan%20(L)%20who%20essayed%20the%20character%20based%20on%20his%20Arjun's%20life%20story%3B%20Arjun%20with%20Shoojit%20Sircar%20(R)%2C%20director%20of%20the%20film%20I%20Want%20to%20Talk%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Farjun-sen-and-battling-cancer-3-1751550919.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Farjun-sen-and-battling-cancer-3-1751550919-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Farjun-sen-and-battling-cancer-3-1751550919-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Farjun-sen-and-battling-cancer-3-1751550919-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Farjun-sen-and-battling-cancer-3-1751550919-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-461685%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EArjun%20with%20Abhishek%20Bachchan%20(L)%20who%20essayed%20the%20character%20based%20on%20his%20Arjun%E2%80%99s%20life%20s